column5: (I know "bigwalleye1" has a post in the Rags thread ....) Can anybody update us on the water level in the area of Lac Seul in Deception Bay?? TIA.
We come in through Hudson landing and not deception but run right by it. Water is low but not as low as it can be. Shouldn't have any issues.
Thank you for your reply. OH --- maybe a MORE important question - How was your fishing up there?
Good fishing. Fished bear paw and canoe and did well. 3 of us had at least a 150 day the other 2 days the wind switched and slowed down to 40+ days.
